Header.title: ECE Outreach
Header.paragraph: Students of Colorado State University bringing Electrical and Computer Engineering to students from middle school to college.

About.paragraph: ECE Outreach is devoted to making Electrical and Computer Engineering more accessible to students by delivering it in small, exciting, and informative packages. Our team works to develop exciting workshops and inspiring demonstrations, opening up the world of electronics to students who may never have considered this exciting path for their education and career.
